reviewText: This movie had been very difficult to find! I was elated to finally get it. I hope you will come up with the Alan Ladd movie; "Hell on Frisco Bay"

This is a bootleg VHS with the commercials and Dialing for Dollars edited out, transferred to DVD.  It's also a first-rate Film Noir starring Alan Ladd.  So take your pick:  suffer the truly wretched transfer process or sit back and enjoy a true classic.
Amazing film with two amazing stars
EXCELLENT FILM NOIR...DONNA REED AND ALAN LADD TO AN EXCELLENT JOB IN MAKING THIS FILM HAPPEN.....A MUST FOR FILM NOIR FILM GOERS...MANY GOOD FLASHBACKS THAT MAKES THIS FILM A SUCCESS...BRAVO
